var book = {
	"name": "Zechariah",
	"numChapters": 14,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>In the eighth month of the second year of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22880A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22880A\"></sup>Darius, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22880B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22880B\"></sup>Zechariah the prophet, the son of Berechiah, the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22880C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22880C\"></sup>Iddo saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was very <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22881D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22881D\"></sup>angry with your fathers.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore say to them, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22882E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22882E\"></sup>Return to Me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, “that I may return to you,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Do not be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22883F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22883F\"></sup>like your fathers, to whom the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22883G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22883G\"></sup>former prophets proclaimed, saying, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22883H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22883H\"></sup>Return now from your evil ways and from your evil deeds.”’ But they did <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22883I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22883I\"></sup>not listen or give heed to Me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22884J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22884J\"></sup>fathers, where are they? And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22884K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22884K\"></sup>prophets, do they live forever?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But did not My words and My statutes, which I commanded My servants the prophets, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22885L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22885L\"></sup>overtake your fathers? Then they repented and said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22885M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22885M\"></sup>As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts purposed to do to us in accordance with our ways and our deeds, so He has dealt with us.’”’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>On the twenty-fourth day of the eleventh month, which is the month Shebat, in the second year of Darius, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Zechariah the prophet, the son of Berechiah, the son of Iddo, as follows:",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I saw at night, and behold, a man was riding on a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22887N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22887N\"></sup>red horse, and he was standing among the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22887O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22887O\"></sup>myrtle trees which were in the ravine, with red, sorrel and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22887P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22887P\"></sup>white horses behind him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then I said, “My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22888Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22888Q\"></sup>lord, what are these?” And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22888R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22888R\"></sup>angel who was speaking with me said to me, “I will show you what these are.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And the man who was standing among the myrtle trees answered and said, “These are those whom the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has sent to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22889S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22889S\"></sup>patrol the earth.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So they answered the angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22890T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22890T\"></sup>standing among the myrtle trees and said, “We have patrolled the earth, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22890U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22890U\"></sup>all the earth is peaceful and quiet.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said, “O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22891V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22891V\"></sup>how long will You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22891W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22891W\"></sup>have no compassion for Jerusalem and the cities of Judah, with which You have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22891X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22891X\"></sup>indignant these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22891Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22891Y\"></sup>seventy years?”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> answered the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22892Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22892Z\"></sup>angel who was speaking with me with gracious words, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22892AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22892AA\"></sup>comforting words.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So the angel who was speaking with me said to me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22893AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22893AB\"></sup>Proclaim, saying, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, “I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22893AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22893AC\"></sup>exceedingly jealous for Jerusalem and Zion.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But I am very <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22894AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22894AD\"></sup>angry with the nations who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22894AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22894AE\"></sup>at ease; for while I was only a little angry, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22894AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22894AF\"></sup>furthered the disaster.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22895AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22895AG\"></sup>return to Jerusalem with compassion; My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22895AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22895AH\"></sup>house will be built in it,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, “and a measuring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22895AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22895AI\"></sup>line will be stretched over Jerusalem.”’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Again, proclaim, saying, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, “My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22896AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22896AJ\"></sup>cities will again overflow with prosperity, and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22896AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22896AK\"></sup>comfort Zion and again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22896AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22896AL\"></sup>choose Jerusalem.”’”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then I lifted up my eyes and looked, and behold, <i>there were</i> four horns.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So I said to the angel who was speaking with me, “What are these?” And he answered me, “These are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22898AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22898AM\"></sup>horns which have scattered Judah, Israel and Jerusalem.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> showed me four <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22899AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22899AN\"></sup>craftsmen.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I said, “What are these coming to do?” And he said, “These are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22900AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22900AO\"></sup>horns which have scattered Judah so that no man lifts up his head; but these <i>craftsmen</i> have come to terrify them, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22900AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22900AP\"></sup>throw down the horns of the nations who have lifted up <i>their</i> horns against the land of Judah in order to scatter it.”"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>Then I lifted up my eyes and looked, and behold, <i>there was</i> a man with a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22901A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22901A\"></sup>measuring line in his hand.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So I said, “Where are you going?” And he said to me, “To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22902B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22902B\"></sup>measure Jerusalem, to see how wide it is and how long it is.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22903C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22903C\"></sup>angel who was speaking with me was going out, and another angel was coming out to meet him,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and said to him, “Run, speak to that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22904D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22904D\"></sup>young man, saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22904E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22904E\"></sup>Jerusalem will be inhabited <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22904F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22904F\"></sup>without walls because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22904G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22904G\"></sup>multitude of men and cattle within it.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For I,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘will be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22905H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22905H\"></sup>wall of fire around her, and I will be the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22905I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22905I\"></sup>glory in her midst.’”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Ho there! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22906J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22906J\"></sup>Flee from the land of the north,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “for I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22906K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22906K\"></sup>dispersed you as the four winds of the heavens,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Ho, Zion! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22907L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22907L\"></sup>Escape, you who are living with the daughter of Babylon.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, “After <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22908M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22908M\"></sup>glory He has sent me against the nations which plunder you, for he who touches you, touches the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22908N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22908N\"></sup>apple of His eye.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For behold, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22909O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22909O\"></sup>wave My hand over them so that they will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22909P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22909P\"></sup>plunder for their slaves. Then you will know that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has sent Me.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22910Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22910Q\"></sup>Sing for joy and be glad, O daughter of Zion; for behold I am coming and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22910R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22910R\"></sup>dwell in your midst,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22911S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22911S\"></sup>Many nations will join themselves to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in that day and will become My people. Then I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22911T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22911T\"></sup>dwell in your midst, and you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22911U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22911U\"></sup>know that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has sent Me to you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22912V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22912V\"></sup>possess Judah as His portion in the holy land, and will again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22912W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22912W\"></sup>choose Jerusalem.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22913X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22913X\"></sup>Be silent, all flesh, before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; for He is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22913Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22913Y\"></sup>aroused from His holy habitation.”"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Then he showed me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22914A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22914A\"></sup>Joshua the high priest standing before the angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22914B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22914B\"></sup>Satan standing at his right hand to accuse him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22915C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22915C\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> rebuke you, Satan! Indeed, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22915D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22915D\"></sup>chosen Jerusalem rebuke you! Is this not a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22915E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22915E\"></sup>brand plucked from the fire?”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Now Joshua was clothed with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22916F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22916F\"></sup>filthy garments and standing before the angel.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He spoke and said to those who were standing before him, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22917G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22917G\"></sup>Remove the filthy garments from him.” Again he said to him, “See, I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22917H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22917H\"></sup>taken your iniquity away from you and will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22917I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22917I\"></sup>clothe you with festal robes.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then I said, “Let them put a clean <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22918J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22918J\"></sup>turban on his head.” So they put a clean turban on his head and clothed him with garments, while the angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was standing by.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And the angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> admonished Joshua, saying,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, ‘If you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22920K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22920K\"></sup>walk in My ways and if you will perform My service, then you will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22920L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22920L\"></sup>govern My house and also have charge of My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22920M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22920M\"></sup>courts, and I will grant you free access among these who are standing <i>here</i>.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Now listen, Joshua the high priest, you and your friends who are sitting in front of you—indeed they are men who are a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22921N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22921N\"></sup>symbol, for behold, I am going to bring in My servant the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22921O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22921O\"></sup>Branch.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For behold, the stone that I have set before Joshua; on one stone are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22922P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22922P\"></sup>seven eyes. Behold, I will engrave an inscription on it,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, ‘and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22922Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22922Q\"></sup>remove the iniquity of that land in one day.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>‘In that day,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, ‘every one of you will invite his neighbor to <i>sit</i> under <i>his</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22923R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22923R\"></sup>vine and under <i>his</i> fig tree.’”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22924A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22924A\"></sup>the angel who was speaking with me returned and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22924B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22924B\"></sup>roused me, as a man who is awakened from his sleep.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He said to me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22925C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22925C\"></sup>What do you see?” And I said, “I see, and behold, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22925D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22925D\"></sup>lampstand all of gold with its bowl on the top of it, and its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22925E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22925E\"></sup>seven lamps on it with seven spouts belonging to each of the lamps which are on the top of it;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22926F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22926F\"></sup>two olive trees by it, one on the right side of the bowl and the other on its left side.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then I said to the angel who was speaking with me saying, “What are these, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22927G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22927G\"></sup>my lord?”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22928H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22928H\"></sup>the angel who was speaking with me answered and said to me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22928I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22928I\"></sup>Do you not know what these are?” And I said, “No, my lord.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then he said to me, “This is the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22929J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22929J\"></sup>Zerubbabel saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22929K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22929K\"></sup>Not by might nor by power, but by My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22929L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22929L\"></sup>Spirit,’ says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>‘What are you, O great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22930M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22930M\"></sup>mountain? Before Zerubbabel <i>you will become</i> a plain; and he will bring forth the top stone with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22930N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22930N\"></sup>shouts of “Grace, grace to it!”’”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Also the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“The hands of Zerubbabel have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22932O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22932O\"></sup>laid the foundation of this house, and his hands will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22932P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22932P\"></sup>finish <i>it</i>. Then you will know that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has sent me to you.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For who has despised the day of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22933Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22933Q\"></sup>small things? But these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22933R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22933R\"></sup>seven will be glad when they see the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22933S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22933S\"></sup>plumb line in the hand of Zerubbabel—<i>these are</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22933T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22933T\"></sup>eyes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22933U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22933U\"></sup>range to and fro throughout the earth.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then I said to him, “What are these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22934V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22934V\"></sup>two olive trees on the right of the lampstand and on its left?”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And I answered the second time and said to him, “What are the two olive branches which are beside the two golden pipes, which empty the golden <i>oil</i> from themselves?”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So he answered me, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22936W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22936W\"></sup>Do you not know what these are?” And I said, “No, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22936X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22936X\"></sup>my lord.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then he said, “These are the two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22937Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22937Y\"></sup>anointed ones who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22937Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22937Z\"></sup>standing by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22937AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22937AA\"></sup>Lord of the whole earth.”"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>Then I lifted up my eyes again and looked, and behold, <i>there was</i> a flying <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22938A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22938A\"></sup>scroll.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he said to me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22939B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22939B\"></sup>What do you see?” And I answered, “I see a flying scroll; its length is twenty cubits and its width ten cubits.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then he said to me, “This is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22940C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22940C\"></sup>curse that is going forth over the face of the whole land; surely everyone who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22940D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22940D\"></sup>steals will be purged away according to the writing on one side, and everyone who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22940E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22940E\"></sup>swears will be purged away according to the writing on the other side.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22941F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22941F\"></sup>make it go forth,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, “and it will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22941G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22941G\"></sup>enter the house of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22941H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22941H\"></sup>thief and the house of the one who swears falsely by My name; and it will spend the night within that house and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22941I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22941I\"></sup>consume it with its timber and stones.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22942J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22942J\"></sup>the angel who was speaking with me went out and said to me, “Lift up now your eyes and see what this is going forth.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I said, “What is it?” And he said, “This is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22943K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22943K\"></sup>ephah going forth.” Again he said, “This is their appearance in all the land",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>(and behold, a lead cover was lifted up); and this is a woman sitting inside the ephah.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then he said, “This is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22945L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22945L\"></sup>Wickedness!” And he threw her down into the middle of the ephah and cast the lead weight on its opening.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then I lifted up my eyes and looked, and there two women were coming out with the wind in their wings; and they had wings like the wings of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22946M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22946M\"></sup>stork, and they lifted up the ephah between the earth and the heavens.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I said to the angel who was speaking with me, “Where are they taking the ephah?”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then he said to me, “To build a temple for her in the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22948N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22948N\"></sup>Shinar; and when it is prepared, she will be set there on her own pedestal.”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Now I lifted up my eyes again and looked, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22949A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22949A\"></sup>four chariots were coming forth from between the two mountains; and the mountains <i>were</i> bronze mountains.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>With the first chariot <i>were</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22950B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22950B\"></sup>red horses, with the second chariot <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22950C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22950C\"></sup>black horses,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>with the third chariot <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22951D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22951D\"></sup>white horses, and with the fourth chariot strong <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22951E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22951E\"></sup>dappled horses.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then I spoke and said to the angel who was speaking with me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22952F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22952F\"></sup>What are these, my lord?”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The angel replied to me, “These are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22953G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22953G\"></sup>four spirits of heaven, going forth after standing before the Lord of all the earth,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>with one of which the black horses are going forth to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22954H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22954H\"></sup>north country; and the white ones go forth after them, while the dappled ones go forth to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22954I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22954I\"></sup>south country.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When the strong ones went out, they were eager to go to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22955J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22955J\"></sup>patrol the earth.” And He said, “Go, patrol the earth.” So they patrolled the earth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then He cried out to me and spoke to me saying, “See, those who are going to the land of the north have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22956K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22956K\"></sup>appeased My wrath in the land of the north.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22957L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22957L\"></sup>word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> also came to me, saying,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22958M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22958M\"></sup>Take <i>an offering</i> from the exiles, from Heldai, Tobijah and Jedaiah; and you go the same day and enter the house of Josiah the son of Zephaniah, where they have arrived from Babylon.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Take silver and gold, make an <i>ornate</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22959N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22959N\"></sup>crown and set <i>it</i> on the head of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22959O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22959O\"></sup>Joshua the son of Jehozadak, the high priest.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then say to him, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, “Behold, a man whose name is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22960P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22960P\"></sup>Branch, for He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22960Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22960Q\"></sup>branch out from where He is; and He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22960R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22960R\"></sup>build the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Yes, it is He who will build the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and He who will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22961S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22961S\"></sup>bear the honor and sit and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22961T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22961T\"></sup>rule on His throne. Thus, He will be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22961U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22961U\"></sup>priest on His throne, and the counsel of peace will be between the two offices.”’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Now the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22962V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22962V\"></sup>crown will become a reminder in the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to Helem, Tobijah, Jedaiah and Hen the son of Zephaniah.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22963W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22963W\"></sup>Those who are far off will come and build the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.” Then you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22963X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22963X\"></sup>know that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has sent me to you. And it will take place if you completely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22963Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22963Y\"></sup>obey the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>In the fourth year of King Darius, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Zechariah on the fourth <i>day</i> of the ninth month, <i>which is</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22964A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22964A\"></sup>Chislev.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Now <i>the town of</i> Bethel had sent Sharezer and Regemmelech and their men to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22965B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22965B\"></sup>seek the favor of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>speaking to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22966C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22966C\"></sup>priests who belong to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, and to the prophets, saying, “Shall I weep in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22966D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22966D\"></sup>fifth month and abstain, as I have done these many years?”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts came to me, saying,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Say to all the people of the land and to the priests, ‘When you fasted and mourned in the fifth and seventh months these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22968E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22968E\"></sup>seventy years, was it actually for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22968F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22968F\"></sup>Me that you fasted?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When you eat and drink, do you not eat for yourselves and do you not drink for yourselves?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Are not <i>these</i> the words which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22970G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22970G\"></sup>proclaimed by the former prophets, when Jerusalem was inhabited and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22970H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22970H\"></sup>prosperous along with its cities around it, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22970I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22970I\"></sup>Negev and the foothills were inhabited?’”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Zechariah saying,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Thus has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22972J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22972J\"></sup>Dispense true justice and practice <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22972K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22972K\"></sup>kindness and compassion each to his brother;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22973L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22973L\"></sup>do not oppress the widow or the orphan, the stranger or the poor; and do <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22973M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22973M\"></sup>not devise evil in your hearts against one another.’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22974N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22974N\"></sup>refused to pay attention and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22974O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22974O\"></sup>turned a stubborn shoulder and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22974P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22974P\"></sup>stopped their ears from hearing.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They made their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22975Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22975Q\"></sup>hearts <i>like</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22975R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22975R\"></sup>flint so that they could not hear the law and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22975S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22975S\"></sup>words which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts had sent by His Spirit through the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22975T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22975T\"></sup>former prophets; therefore great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22975U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22975U\"></sup>wrath came from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22976V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22976V\"></sup>He called and they would not listen, so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22976W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22976W\"></sup>they called and I would not listen,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“but I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22977X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22977X\"></sup>scattered them with a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22977Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22977Y\"></sup>storm wind among all the nations whom they have not known. Thus the land is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22977Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22977Z\"></sup>desolated behind them so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22977AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22977AA\"></sup>no one went back and forth, for they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22977AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22977AB\"></sup>made the pleasant land desolate.”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts came, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, ‘I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22979A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22979A\"></sup>exceedingly jealous for Zion, yes, with great wrath I am jealous for her.’",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘I will return to Zion and will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22980B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22980B\"></sup>dwell in the midst of Jerusalem. Then Jerusalem will be called the City of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22980C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22980C\"></sup>Truth, and the mountain of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts <i>will be called</i> the Holy Mountain.’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22981D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22981D\"></sup>Old men and old women will again sit in the streets of Jerusalem, each man with his staff in his hand because of age.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And the streets of the city will be filled with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22982E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22982E\"></sup>boys and girls playing in its streets.’",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, ‘If it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22983F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22983F\"></sup>too difficult in the sight of the remnant of this people in those days, will it also be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22983G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22983G\"></sup>too difficult in My sight?’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, ‘Behold, I am going to save My people from the land of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22984H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22984H\"></sup>east and from the land of the west;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22985I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22985I\"></sup>bring them <i>back</i> and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22985J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22985J\"></sup>live in the midst of Jerusalem; and they shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22985K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22985K\"></sup>My people, and I will be their God in truth and righteousness.’",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, ‘Let your hands be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22986L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22986L\"></sup>strong, you who are listening in these days to these words from the mouth of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22986M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22986M\"></sup>prophets, <i>those</i> who <i>spoke</i> in the day that the foundation of the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts was laid, to the end that the temple might be built.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For before those days there was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22987N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22987N\"></sup>no wage for man or any wage for animal; and for him who went out or came in there was no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22987O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22987O\"></sup>peace because of his enemies, and I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22987P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22987P\"></sup>set all men one against another.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But now I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22988Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22988Q\"></sup>not treat the remnant of this people as in the former days,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>‘For <i>there will be</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22989R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22989R\"></sup>peace for the seed: the vine will yield its fruit, the land will yield its produce and the heavens will give their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22989S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22989S\"></sup>dew; and I will cause the remnant of this people to inherit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22989T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22989T\"></sup>all these <i>things</i>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>It will come about that just as you were a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22990U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22990U\"></sup>curse among the nations, O house of Judah and house of Israel, so I will save you that you may become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22990V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22990V\"></sup>blessing. Do not fear; let your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22990W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22990W\"></sup>hands be strong.’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, ‘Just as I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22991X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22991X\"></sup>purposed to do harm to you when your fathers provoked Me to wrath,’ says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, ‘and I have not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22991Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22991Y\"></sup>relented,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>so I have again purposed in these days to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22992Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22992Z\"></sup>do good to Jerusalem and to the house of Judah. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22992AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22992AA\"></sup>Do not fear!",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>These are the things which you should do: speak the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22993AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22993AB\"></sup>truth to one another; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22993AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22993AC\"></sup>judge with truth and judgment for peace in your gates.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Also let none of you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22994AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22994AD\"></sup>devise evil in your heart against another, and do not love <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22994AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22994AE\"></sup>perjury; for all these are what I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22994AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22994AF\"></sup>hate,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts came to me, saying,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, ‘The fast of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22996AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22996AG\"></sup>fourth, the fast of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22996AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22996AH\"></sup>fifth, the fast of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22996AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22996AI\"></sup>seventh and the fast of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22996AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22996AJ\"></sup>tenth <i>months</i> will become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22996AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22996AK\"></sup>joy, gladness, and cheerful feasts for the house of Judah; so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22996AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22996AL\"></sup>love truth and peace.’",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, ‘<i>It will</i> yet <i>be</i> that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22997AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22997AM\"></sup>peoples will come, even the inhabitants of many cities.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The inhabitants of one will go to another, saying, “Let us go at once to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22998AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22998AN\"></sup>entreat the favor of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and to seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts; I will also go.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22999AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22999AO\"></sup>many peoples and mighty nations will come to seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts in Jerusalem and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22999AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22999AP\"></sup>entreat the favor of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, ‘In those days ten men from all the nations will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23000AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23000AQ\"></sup>grasp the garment of a Jew, saying, “Let us go with you, for we have heard that God is with you.”’”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>The burden of the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is against the land of Hadrach, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23001A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23001A\"></sup>Damascus as its resting place (for the eyes of men, especially of all the tribes of Israel, are toward the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>),",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23002B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23002B\"></sup>Hamath also, which borders on it;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23002C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23002C\"></sup>Tyre and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23002D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23002D\"></sup>Sidon, though they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23002E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23002E\"></sup>very wise.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For Tyre built herself a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23003F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23003F\"></sup>fortressAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23003G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23003G\"></sup>piled up silver like dust,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23003H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23003H\"></sup>gold like the mire of the streets.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Behold, the Lord will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23004I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23004I\"></sup>dispossess herAnd cast her wealth into the sea;And she will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23004J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23004J\"></sup>consumed with fire.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Ashkelon will see <i>it</i> and be afraid.Gaza too will writhe in great pain;Also Ekron, for her expectation has been confounded.Moreover, the king will perish from Gaza,And Ashkelon will not be inhabited.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And a mongrel race will dwell in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23006K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23006K\"></sup>Ashdod,And I will cut off the pride of the Philistines.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And I will remove their blood from their mouthAnd their detestable things from between their teeth.Then they also will be a remnant for our God,And be like a clan in Judah,And Ekron like a Jebusite.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But I will camp around My house because of an army,Because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23008L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23008L\"></sup>him who passes by and returns;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23008M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23008M\"></sup>no oppressor will pass over them anymore,For now I have seen with My eyes.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23009N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23009N\"></sup>Rejoice greatly, O daughter of Zion!Shout <i>in triumph</i>, O daughter of Jerusalem!Behold, your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23009O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23009O\"></sup>king is coming to you;He is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23009P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23009P\"></sup>just and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23009Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23009Q\"></sup>endowed with salvation,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23009R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23009R\"></sup>Humble, and mounted on a donkey,Even on a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23009S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23009S\"></sup>colt, the foal of a donkey.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23010T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23010T\"></sup>cut off the chariot from EphraimAnd the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23010U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23010U\"></sup>horse from Jerusalem;And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23010V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23010V\"></sup>bow of war will be cut off.And He will speak <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23010W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23010W\"></sup>peace to the nations;And His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23010X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23010X\"></sup>dominion will be from sea to sea,And from the River to the ends of the earth.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>As for you also, because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23011Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23011Y\"></sup>blood of <i>My</i> covenant with you,I have set your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23011Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23011Z\"></sup>prisoners free from the waterless pit.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Return to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23012AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23012AA\"></sup>stronghold, O prisoners who have the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23012AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23012AB\"></sup>hope;This very day I am declaring that I will restore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23012AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23012AC\"></sup>double to you.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23013AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23013AD\"></sup>bend Judah as My bow,I will fill the bow with Ephraim.And I will stir up your sons, O Zion, against your sons, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23013AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23013AE\"></sup>Greece;And I will make you like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23013AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23013AF\"></sup>warrior’s sword.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will appear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23014AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23014AG\"></sup>over them,And His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23014AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23014AH\"></sup>arrow will go forth like lightning;And the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> will blow the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23014AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23014AI\"></sup>trumpet,And will march in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23014AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23014AJ\"></sup>storm winds of the south.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23015AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23015AK\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts will defend them.And they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23015AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23015AL\"></sup>devour and trample on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23015AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23015AM\"></sup>sling stones;And they will drink <i>and</i> be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23015AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23015AN\"></sup>boisterous as with wine;And they will be filled like a <i>sacrificial</i> basin,<i>Drenched</i> like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23015AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23015AO\"></sup>corners of the altar.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23016AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23016AP\"></sup>save them in that dayAs the flock of His people;For <i>they are as</i> the stones of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23016AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23016AQ\"></sup>crown,Sparkling in His land.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23017AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23017AR\"></sup>comeliness and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23017AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23017AS\"></sup>beauty <i>will be</i> theirs!Grain will make the young men flourish, and new wine the virgins."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Ask <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23018A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23018A\"></sup>rain from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> at the time of the spring rain—The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23018B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23018B\"></sup>makes the storm clouds;And He will give them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23018C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23018C\"></sup>showers of rain, vegetation in the field to <i>each</i> man.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23019D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23019D\"></sup>teraphim speak iniquity,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23019E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23019E\"></sup>diviners see lying visionsAnd tell <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23019F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23019F\"></sup>false dreams;They comfort in vain.Therefore <i>the people</i> wander like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23019G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23019G\"></sup>sheep,They are afflicted, because there is no shepherd.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23020H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23020H\"></sup>anger is kindled against the shepherds,And I will punish the male goats;For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23020I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23020I\"></sup>visited His flock, the house of Judah,And will make them like His majestic horse in battle.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“From them will come the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23021J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23021J\"></sup>cornerstone,From them the tent peg,From them the bow of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23021K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23021K\"></sup>battle,From them every ruler, <i>all</i> of them together.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“They will be as mighty men,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23022L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23022L\"></sup>Treading down <i>the enemy</i> in the mire of the streets in battle;And they will fight, for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <i>will be</i> with them;And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23022M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23022M\"></sup>riders on horses will be put to shame.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23023N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23023N\"></sup>strengthen the house of Judah,And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23023O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23023O\"></sup>save the house of Joseph,And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23023P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23023P\"></sup>bring them back,Because I have had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23023Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23023Q\"></sup>compassion on them;And they will be as though I had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23023R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23023R\"></sup>not rejected them,For I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23023S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23023S\"></sup>answer them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Ephraim will be like a mighty man,And their heart will be glad as if <i>from</i> wine;Indeed, their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23024T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23024T\"></sup>children will see <i>it</i> and be glad,Their heart will rejoice in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23025U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23025U\"></sup>whistle for them to gather them together,For I have redeemed them;And they will be as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23025V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23025V\"></sup>numerous as they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23025W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23025W\"></sup>were before.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“When I scatter them among the peoples,They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23026X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23026X\"></sup>remember Me in far countries,And they with their children will live and come back.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23027Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23027Y\"></sup>bring them back from the land of EgyptAnd gather them from Assyria;And I will bring them into the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23027Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23027Z\"></sup>Gilead and LebanonUntil <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23027AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23027AA\"></sup>no <i>room</i> can be found for them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“And they will pass through the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23028AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23028AB\"></sup>sea <i>of</i> distressAnd He will strike the waves in the sea,So that all the depths of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23028AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23028AC\"></sup>Nile will dry up;And the pride of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23028AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23028AD\"></sup>Assyria will be brought downAnd the scepter of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23028AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23028AE\"></sup>Egypt will depart.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23029AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23029AF\"></sup>strengthen them in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And in His name <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23029AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23029AG\"></sup>they will walk,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Open your doors, O Lebanon,That a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23030A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23030A\"></sup>fire may feed on your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23030B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23030B\"></sup>cedars.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Wail, O cypress, for the cedar has fallen,Because the glorious <i>trees</i> have been destroyed;Wail, O oaks of Bashan,For the impenetrable forest has come down.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>There is a sound of the shepherds’ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23032C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23032C\"></sup>wail,For their glory is ruined;There is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23032D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23032D\"></sup>sound of the young lions’ roar,For the pride of the Jordan is ruined.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> my God, “Pasture the flock <i>doomed</i> to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23033E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23033E\"></sup>slaughter.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Those who buy them slay them and go <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23034F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23034F\"></sup>unpunished, and <i>each of</i> those who sell them says, ‘Blessed be the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23034G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23034G\"></sup>I have become rich!’ And their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23034H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23034H\"></sup>own shepherds have no pity on them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23035I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23035I\"></sup>no longer have pity on the inhabitants of the land,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; “but behold, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23035J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23035J\"></sup>cause the men to fall, each into another’s power and into the power of his king; and they will strike the land, and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23035K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23035K\"></sup>not deliver <i>them</i> from their power.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23036L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23036L\"></sup>pastured the flock <i>doomed</i> to slaughter, hence the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23036M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23036M\"></sup>afflicted of the flock. And I took for myself two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23036N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23036N\"></sup>staffs: the one I called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23036O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23036O\"></sup>Favor and the other I called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23036P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23036P\"></sup>Union; so I pastured the flock.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then I annihilated the three shepherds in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23037Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23037Q\"></sup>one month, for my soul was impatient with them, and their soul also was weary of me.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then I said, “I will not pasture you. What is to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23038R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23038R\"></sup>die, let it die, and what is to be annihilated, let it be annihilated; and let those who are left eat one another’s flesh.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I took my staff <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23039S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23039S\"></sup>Favor and cut it in pieces, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23039T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23039T\"></sup>break my covenant which I had made with all the peoples.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So it was broken on that day, and thus the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23040U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23040U\"></sup>afflicted of the flock who were watching me realized that it was the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I said to them, “If it is good in your sight, give <i>me</i> my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23041V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23041V\"></sup>wages; but if not, never mind!” So they weighed out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23041W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23041W\"></sup>thirty <i>shekels</i> of silver as my wages.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Throw it to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23042X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23042X\"></sup>potter, <i>that</i> magnificent price at which I was valued by them.” So I took the thirty <i>shekels</i> of silver and threw them to the potter in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then I cut in pieces my second staff <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23043Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23043Y\"></sup>Union, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23043Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23043Z\"></sup>break the brotherhood between Judah and Israel.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Take again for yourself the equipment of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23044AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23044AA\"></sup>foolish shepherd.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For behold, I am going to raise up a shepherd in the land who will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23045AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23045AB\"></sup>not care for the perishing, seek the scattered, heal the broken, or sustain the one standing, but will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23045AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23045AC\"></sup>devour the flesh of the fat <i>sheep</i> and tear off their hoofs.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23046AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23046AD\"></sup>Woe to the worthless shepherdWho leaves the flock!A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23046AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23046AE\"></sup>sword will be on his armAnd on his right eye!His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23046AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23046AF\"></sup>arm will be totally witheredAnd his right eye will be blind.”"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>The burden of the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning Israel.<i>Thus</i> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23047A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23047A\"></sup>stretches out the heavens, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23047B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23047B\"></sup>lays the foundation of the earth, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23047C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23047C\"></sup>forms the spirit of man within him,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Behold, I am going to make Jerusalem a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23048D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23048D\"></sup>cup that causes reeling to all the peoples around; and when the siege is against Jerusalem, it will also be against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23048E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23048E\"></sup>Judah.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>It will come about in that day that I will make Jerusalem a heavy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23049F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23049F\"></sup>stone for all the peoples; all who lift it will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23049G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23049G\"></sup>severely injured. And all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23049H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23049H\"></sup>nations of the earth will be gathered against it.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>In that day,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “I will strike every horse with bewilderment and his rider with madness. But I will watch over the house of Judah, while I strike every horse of the peoples with blindness.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the clans of Judah will say in their hearts, ‘A strong support for us are the inhabitants of Jerusalem through the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, their God.’",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“In that day I will make the clans of Judah like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23052I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23052I\"></sup>firepot among pieces of wood and a flaming torch among sheaves, so they will consume on the right hand and on the left all the surrounding peoples, while the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23052J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23052J\"></sup>inhabitants of Jerusalem again dwell on their own sites in Jerusalem.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> also will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23053K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23053K\"></sup>save the tents of Judah first, so that the glory of the house of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23053L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23053L\"></sup>David and the glory of the inhabitants of Jerusalem will not be magnified above Judah.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>In that day the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23054M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23054M\"></sup>defend the inhabitants of Jerusalem, and the one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23054N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23054N\"></sup>is feeble among them in that day will be like David, and the house of David <i>will be</i> like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23054O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23054O\"></sup>God, like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23054P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23054P\"></sup>angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> before them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And in that day I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23055Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23055Q\"></sup>set about to destroy all the nations that come against Jerusalem.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23056R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23056R\"></sup>pour out on the house of David and on the inhabitants of Jerusalem, the Spirit of grace and of supplication, so that they will look on Me whom they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23056S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23056S\"></sup>pierced; and they will mourn for Him, as one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23056T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23056T\"></sup>mourns for an only son, and they will weep bitterly over Him like the bitter weeping over a firstborn.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>In that day there will be great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23057U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23057U\"></sup>mourning in Jerusalem, like the mourning of Hadadrimmon in the plain of Megiddo.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The land will mourn, every family by itself; the family of the house of David by itself and their wives by themselves; the family of the house of Nathan by itself and their wives by themselves;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>the family of the house of Levi by itself and their wives by themselves; the family of the Shimeites by itself and their wives by themselves;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>all the families that remain, every family by itself and their wives by themselves."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>“In that day a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23061A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23061A\"></sup>fountain will be opened for the house of David and for the inhabitants of Jerusalem, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23061B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23061B\"></sup>sin and for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23061C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23061C\"></sup>impurity.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“It will come about in that day,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, “that I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23062D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23062D\"></sup>cut off the names of the idols from the land, and they will no longer be remembered; and I will also remove the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23062E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23062E\"></sup>prophets and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23062F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23062F\"></sup>unclean spirit from the land.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And if anyone still <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23063G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23063G\"></sup>prophesies, then his father and mother who gave birth to him will say to him, ‘You shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23063H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23063H\"></sup>not live, for you have spoken <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23063I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23063I\"></sup>falsely in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’; and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23063J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23063J\"></sup>father and mother who gave birth to him will pierce him through when he prophesies.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Also it will come about in that day that the prophets will each be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23064K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23064K\"></sup>ashamed of his vision when he prophesies, and they will not put on a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23064L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23064L\"></sup>hairy robe in order to deceive;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>but he will say, ‘I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23065M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23065M\"></sup>not a prophet; I am a tiller of the ground, for a man sold me as a slave in my youth.’",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And one will say to him, ‘What are these wounds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23066N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23066N\"></sup>between your arms?’ Then he will say, ‘<i>Those</i> with which I was wounded in the house of my friends.’",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Awake, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23067O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23067O\"></sup>sword, against My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23067P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23067P\"></sup>Shepherd,And against the man, My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23067Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23067Q\"></sup>Associate,”Declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23067R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23067R\"></sup>Strike the Shepherd that the sheep may be scattered;And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23067S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23067S\"></sup>turn My hand against the little ones.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“It will come about in all the land,”Declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“That <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23068T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23068T\"></sup>two parts in it will be cut off <i>and</i> perish;But the third will be left in it.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“And I will bring the third part through the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23069U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23069U\"></sup>fire,Refine them as silver is refined,And test them as gold is tested.They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23069V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23069V\"></sup>call on My name,And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23069W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23069W\"></sup>answer them;I will say, ‘They are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23069X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23069X\"></sup>My people,’And they will say, ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is my God.’”"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>Behold, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23070A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23070A\"></sup>day is coming for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23070B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23070B\"></sup>the spoil taken from you will be divided among you.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23071C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23071C\"></sup>gather all the nations against Jerusalem to battle, and the city will be captured, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23071D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23071D\"></sup>houses plundered, the women ravished and half of the city exiled, but the rest of the people will not be cut off from the city.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will go forth and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23072E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23072E\"></sup>fight against those nations, as when He fights on a day of battle.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>In that day His feet will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23073F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23073F\"></sup>stand on the Mount of Olives, which is in front of Jerusalem on the east; and the Mount of Olives will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23073G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23073G\"></sup>split in its middle from east to west by a very large valley, so that half of the mountain will move toward the north and the other half toward the south.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You will flee by the valley of My mountains, for the valley of the mountains will reach to Azel; yes, you will flee just as you fled before the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23074H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23074H\"></sup>earthquake in the days of Uzziah king of Judah. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23074I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23074I\"></sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, my God, will come, <i>and</i> all the holy ones with Him!",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>In that day there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23075J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23075J\"></sup>no light; the luminaries will dwindle.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For it will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23076K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23076K\"></sup>a unique day which is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23076L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23076L\"></sup>known to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, neither day nor night, but it will come about that at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23076M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23076M\"></sup>evening time there will be light.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And in that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23077N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23077N\"></sup>living waters will flow out of Jerusalem, half of them toward the eastern sea and the other half toward the western sea; it will be in summer as well as in winter.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23078O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23078O\"></sup>king over all the earth; in that day the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be <i>the only</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23078P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23078P\"></sup>one, and His name <i>the only</i> one.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>All the land will be changed into a plain from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23079Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23079Q\"></sup>Geba to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23079R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23079R\"></sup>Rimmon south of Jerusalem; but Jerusalem will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23079S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23079S\"></sup>rise and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23079T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23079T\"></sup>remain on its site from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23079U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23079U\"></sup>Benjamin’s Gate as far as the place of the First Gate to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23079V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23079V\"></sup>Corner Gate, and from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23079W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23079W\"></sup>Tower of Hananel to the king’s wine presses.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>People will live in it, and there will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23080X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23080X\"></sup>no longer be a curse, for Jerusalem will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23080Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23080Y\"></sup>dwell in security.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Now this will be the plague with which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will strike all the peoples who have gone to war against Jerusalem; their flesh will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23081Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23081Z\"></sup>rot while they stand on their feet, and their eyes will rot in their sockets, and their tongue will rot in their mouth.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>It will come about in that day that a great panic from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will fall on them; and they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23082AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23082AA\"></sup>seize one another’s hand, and the hand of one will be lifted against the hand of another.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23083AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23083AB\"></sup>Judah also will fight at Jerusalem; and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23083AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23083AC\"></sup>wealth of all the surrounding nations will be gathered, gold and silver and garments in great abundance.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So also like this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23084AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23084AD\"></sup>plague will be the plague on the horse, the mule, the camel, the donkey and all the cattle that will be in those camps.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then it will come about that any who are left of all the nations that went against Jerusalem will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23085AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23085AE\"></sup>go up from year to year to worship the King, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, and to celebrate the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23085AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23085AF\"></sup>Feast of Booths.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And it will be that whichever of the families of the earth does not go up to Jerusalem to worship the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23086AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23086AG\"></sup>King, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23086AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23086AH\"></sup>no rain on them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>If the family of Egypt does not go up or enter, then no <i>rain will fall</i> on them; it will be the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23087AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23087AI\"></sup>plague with which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> smites the nations who do not go up to celebrate the Feast of Booths.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>This will be the punishment of Egypt, and the punishment of all the nations who do not go up to celebrate the Feast of Booths.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>In that day there will <i>be inscribed</i> on the bells of the horses, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23089AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23089AJ\"></sup>HOLY TO THE LORD.” And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23089AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23089AK\"></sup>cooking pots in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> house will be like the bowls before the altar.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Every cooking pot in Jerusalem and in Judah will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23090AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23090AL\"></sup>holy to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts; and all who sacrifice will come and take of them and boil in them. And there will no longer be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23090AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23090AM\"></sup>Canaanite in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts in that day."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;